info.description:
API collection for the Ali Real Estate Conversational AI system.

Local server: http://localhost:8000
WebSocket: ws://localhost:8000/ws/chat

WebSocket payload format:
  → Client: {"session_id": "<uuid>", "message": "<text>", "voice": true|false}
  ← Server: {"type": "token|done|state|error|audio_chunk|session_created", "data": "..."}
